  "title": "Path-Dependence in Form",
  "concept": "A structure shaped under one set of conditions persists when conditions change, carrying its original design into new contexts—history constrains what comes next.",
  "interactiveId": "d3f33bf6-3a7d-48c3-bde7-f16b15ba28ed",
  "sourcePieceId": "f4c864dd-c622-421f-844d-2c8b39ea4430",
  "publishedAt": 1778441667657,
  "voiceScore": 88,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Path-Dependence in Form</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --early: #c9a227;\n    --late: #1a6b62;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .timeline-container {\n    margin: 24px 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n  }\n  .timeline-label {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n  }\n  .timeline-track {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 60px;\n    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--early) 0%, var(--early) 50%, var(--late) 50%, var(--late) 100%);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  }\n  .timeline-marker {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n    width: 2px;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\n    pointer-events: none;\n  }\n  .timeline-marker::after {\n    content: \"Conditions change\";\n    position: absolute;\n    top: -24px;\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translateX(-50%);\n    font-size: 0.7rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n  .timeline-control {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n  }\n  .timeline-control label {\n    font-weight: 500;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .timeline-control input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    accent-color: var(--fg);\n    min-width: 120px;\n  }\n  .timeline-control output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 3ch;\n    text-align: right;\n  }\n  .structure-display {\n    margin: 20px 0;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n  .feature-box {\n    padding: 14px;\n    background: var(--bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n  }\n  .feature-header {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .feature-list {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 6px;\n  }\n  .feature-item {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n  }\n  .feature-dot {\n    width: 8px;\n    height: 8px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .dot-early {\n    background: var(--early);\n  }\n  .dot-late {\n    background: var(--late);\n  }\n  .dot-inherited {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--early) 50%, var(--late) 50%);\n  }\n  .reading {\n    margin: 18px 0 6px;\n    padding: 10px 14px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .reading strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .structure-display {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n    .timeline-control {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n    }\n    .timeline-control input[type=range] {\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Drag to set when the structure freezes</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Early conditions build the form. Later conditions must work with what already exists.</p>\n\n<div class=\"timeline-container\">\n  <div class=\"timeline-label\">Timeline</div>\n  <div class=\"timeline-track\">\n    <div class=\"timeline-marker\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"timeline-control\">\n    <label for=\"freeze-point\">Structure freezes at time:</label>\n    <input id=\"freeze-point\" type=\"range\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"35\" aria-describedby=\"freeze-out\">\n    <output id=\"freeze-out\" for=\"freeze-point\">35</output>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"structure-display\">\n  <div class=\"feature-box\">\n    <div class=\"feature-header\">Features present</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-list\" id=\"features-present\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"feature-box\">\n    <div class=\"feature-header\">Context</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-list\" id=\"context-info\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"reading\">\n  Structure shaped by: <strong id=\"shaped-by\">early conditions</strong>.<br>\n  Now operates in: <strong id=\"operates-in\">later conditions</strong>.\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">The form carries its history. What was built early persists even when the world changes.</p>\n\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    var slider = document.getElementById('freeze-point');\n    var freezeOut = document.getElementById('freeze-out');\n    var featuresPresent = document.getElementById('features-present');\n    var contextInfo = document.getElementById('context-info');\n    var shapedBy = document.getElementById('shaped-by');\n    var operatesIn = document.getElementById('operates-in');\n    var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n    var earlyFeatures = [\n      'Rigid segments',\n      'Weight-bearing joints',\n      'Articulated connections',\n      'Proportions for support'\n    ];\n\n    var lateFeatures = [\n      'Flexible appendages',\n      'Buoyancy-optimized mass',\n      'Flow-adapted surfaces',\n      'Reduced skeletal density'\n    ];\n\n    function renderFeatures(list, container, dotClass) {\n      container.innerHTML = '';\n      list.forEach(function(text) {\n        var item = document.createElement('div');\n        item.className = 'feature-item';\n        var dot = document.createElement('div');\n        dot.className = 'feature-dot ' + dotClass;\n        var label = document.createElement('span');\n        label.textContent = text;\n        item.appendChild(dot);\n        item.appendChild(label);\n        container.appendChild(item);\n      });\n    }\n\n    function renderContext(lines, container) {\n      container.innerHTML = '';\n      lines.forEach(function(text) {\n        var item = document.createElement('div');\n        item.className = 'feature-item';\n        var label = document.createElement('span');\n        label.textContent = text;\n        item.appendChild(label);\n        container.appendChild(item);\n      });\n    }\n\n    function update() {\n      var t = +slider.value;\n      freezeOut.textContent = t;\n\n      if (t < 20) {\n        // Structure forms very early, almost entirely under early conditions.\n        renderFeatures(earlyFeatures, featuresPresent, 'dot-early');\n        renderContext(['Formed in early context', 'Now in late context', 'Minimal new adaptation'], contextInfo);\n        shapedBy.textContent = 'early conditions almost entirely';\n        operatesIn.textContent = 'late conditions';\n        caption.textContent = 'Built early, before the shift. The structure is locked in—it carries almost no trace of the later world.';\n      } else if (t < 45) {\n        // Structure forms mostly under early conditions, but close to the transition.\n        // Early features dominate, but the form is about to face new context.\n        renderFeatures(earlyFeatures, featuresPresent, 'dot-early');\n        renderContext(['Formed near the transition', 'Carries early design into late context'], contextInfo);\n        shapedBy.textContent = 'early conditions';\n        operatesIn.textContent = 'late conditions';\n        caption.textContent = 'The form carries its history. What was built early persists even when the world changes.';\n      } else if (t < 55) {\n        // Structure freezes right at the transition—hybrid case.\n        // Some early features persist, some late features begin to appear.\n        var mixed = [\n          'Rigid segments (early)',\n          'Weight-bearing joints (early)',\n          'Flow-adapted surfaces (late)',\n          'Buoyancy-optimized mass (late)'\n        ];\n        renderFeatures(mixed, featuresPresent, 'dot-inherited');\n        renderContext(['Formed during the shift', 'Compromise between both worlds'], contextInfo);\n        shapedBy.textContent = 'both conditions';\n        operatesIn.textContent = 'late conditions';\n        caption.textContent = 'Caught mid-transition. The structure reflects both eras—neither fully adapted to one nor the other.';\n      } else if (t < 80) {\n        // Structure freezes after the transition but not at the end.\n        // Late features dominate, but some early legacy remains.\n        var mostlyLate = [\n          'Flexible appendages',\n          'Buoyancy-optimized mass',\n          'Flow-adapted surfaces',\n          'Rigid segments (inherited)'\n        ];\n        renderFeatures(mostlyLate, featuresPresent, 'dot-late');\n        renderContext(['Formed in late context', 'Some early features persist as legacy'], contextInfo);\n        shapedBy.textContent = 'late conditions mostly';\n        operatesIn.textContent = 'late conditions';\n        caption.textContent = 'Mostly adapted to the new world, but traces of the old design remain embedded in the form.';\n      } else {\n        // Structure forms very late, almost entirely under late conditions.\n        renderFeatures(lateFeatures, featuresPresent, 'dot-late');\n        renderContext(['Formed in late context', 'Fully adapted to current conditions'], contextInfo);\n        shapedBy.textContent = 'late conditions almost entirely';\n        operatesIn.textContent = 'late conditions';\n        caption.textContent = 'Built after the shift. The structure is optimized for the world it operates in—no historical baggage.';\n      }\n    }\n\n    slider.addEventListener('input', update);\n    update();\n  })();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
